  <!-- ═══ SENSITIVITY ANALYSIS ═══ -->
  <h2>Sensitivity Analysis</h2>
  <p>Our base case uses 2% growth and a 9% discount rate. But reasonable people disagree on these numbers. Here's what the intrinsic value looks like under different assumptions. Find the combination you believe in.</p>

